{"tid":1975782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家重記得呢段幾個月前臺灣嘅影片","createTime":"2020-04-16T19:04:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T19:19:44.000Z","uid":208722,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b443d0766b2628a9a8f79b031d992c2be2e53457","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:04:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ykcVIQMrc4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FykcVIQMrc4A&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10A9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=a58f8be6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ykcVIQMrc4A</a><br />\n<br />\n再睇睇我哋今時今日做緊乜？<br />\n台灣人相信我哋、對我哋有信心；亦都唔止台灣，重有好多國家嘅人，仍然深信我哋可以成功抵抗中國暴政。我哋係咪應該爭氣啲，繼續團結一致，去成就香港嘅榮光？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">願    我們因為團結感到光榮</span>"},{"pid":"ae5ec1325be063773af754d2a41e7770ae397284","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:05:44.000Z","msg":"事隔三個月重睇一次，馬尿係咁流"},{"pid":"2dd7a1882f7f65268b16e1992abd6703db308f78","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:09:47.000Z","msg":"寧靜嘅生活，唔係理所當然；都已經咁田地，黃圈又何苦內鬥？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">鬥贏對方，支共都只會兩邊都連根拔起</span>"},{"pid":"477c6260f646e604114b83d890d104b472dfab46","tid":1975782,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21999b53d8fe4d330abfd4c7534a9efb776188e2","tid":1975782,"uid":354311,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:10:47.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂你哋香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為個臺灣人都覺得你哋之前好撚團結<br />\n希望依家嘅黃絲唔好再鬥喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0db03df7fceb7f53a8551fd63c60175a8ea587a","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:10:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n願<br />\n我們因為團結感到光榮<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"fca5ccfb53503b3017ce4aa0eb82079bb2da0aaa","tid":1975782,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:12:14.000Z","msg":"保護香港本土文化<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">香 港 國 寶 ： 許冠傑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1973620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1973620</a></div>"},{"pid":"90064bb0878b8f16dca81b3afdfab5b04295ec00","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:12:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n願<br />\n我們因為團結感到光榮<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a636f9a0befc9efc189003d591688a16b183b83b","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:16:32.000Z","msg":"今年，台灣人用自己方式抵抗中國侵犯，贏得世界掌聲；<br />\n<br />\n今年，我哋就反而愈變愈分崩離析，落得藍畜嘲笑。<br />\n<br />\n甘心咩？"},{"pid":"1ed8dc14ae286237ddb51ef7fbff34d6306eaed6","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:17:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77fef235247443b59ef7bd48aed5f994d2cf019e","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:18:53.000Z","msg":"反思、改善係我哋一路以嚟嘅思想武器<br />\n<br />\n要破敵方散播混亂嘅訊息，我哋就真係要做到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">多思考，少妄語</span>"},{"pid":"8c3ebbbe5a2e8feb86d1a27df7e0cb12d30c33c8","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:19:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"078dd350c398ed5e5d86ae352ef00869f74794fd","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:22:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"acdc3ef94a6273b3ce5b3614c680ebc858610e31","tid":1975782,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:23:49.000Z","msg":"為咗打機，香港人真係好撚可愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1965169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1965169</a><br />