r />\n<br />\n臺灣，由上年嘅外交低潮、內政動蕩，到今日成功為民抗疫，成為世界焦點。當日我哋睇住臺灣人選擇一條成功嘅路，到而家台灣人睇住我哋，我哋都應該行出條成功嘅路，報答臺灣人支持。"},{"pid":"65f74afc7a02821a8addfa5105e60937521d6b17","tid":1975782,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T18:28:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5525d73035cdae7943cec4b384d1a75e7dace74b","tid":1975782,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T18:35:22.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}